title: QUIZ! Leicester become 50th team to reach Champions League quarter-finals… can you name all 50?
text:
Leicester become the 50th team to reach the last eight of Europe's biggest competition (Photo: Laurence Griffiths) Share Get daily updates directly to your inbox + Subscribe Could not subscribe, try again later Invalid Email 
Leicester's incredible march into the Champions League quarter-finals is remarkable for a number of reasons. 
The fantastic 2-0 win against Sevilla which put the Foxes into the last eight has not only got people wondering how Barcelona or Real Madrid might cope at King Power. It also saw a new Champions League landmark reached. 
Leicester just became the 50th team to reach the quarter-finals since the current Champions League format was introduced in 1994. 
The question is, how many of those 50 teams can you name? Leicester fans: happy. Very, very happy (Photo: Plumb Images) Read More
